claim.claim-text:
1. An aerial banner assembly for an aircraft, the banner assembly comprising:
a banner adapted to display advertising thereon;
a banner rod attached to a front end of the banner;
a banner spider attached to the banner rod;
a tow rope having a first end attached to the banner spider and a second end adapted to be attached to the aircraft;
and at least two round disks rotatably mounted on the banner rod which provide running wheels.
